<p>We always think that the more we get, the happier we are.
In fact,it dose not.
On the contrary, the fewer we have, the happier we are.</p>

<p>I want to talk about the tourism today.</p>

<p>I feel tired about doing the travel raiders, buying preparations, carrying almost everything,  so-called tourism. In fact, it is disgusting.
Trip is the heart journey. If we make a simple journey:
1) you will meet different situation out of you expected;
2) Stop when u want, listen to the voice of the heart;
3) limited access to iPad, computer etc, then u will relax entirely.</p>

<p>Here is the suggestions of simple journey:
1) Besides of the visa, tickets, no more homework, enjoy the surprises and reconcile in new place;
2) carried a bag, clothing, Kindle and a mobile phone if u need ,then nothing else;
3) Then start your trip.</p>

<p>Have fun.</p>
<!-- content end -->
